metadata.name: CHRISTMAS CRACKER (OE BURN)
metadata.description:
Burn will open for you to crack your cracker; 

White partyhat = Burn 4 Crackers  
Blue partyhat = Burn 6 Crackers  
Red partyhat = Burn 3 Crackers  
Green partyhat = Burn 2 Crackers  
Yellow partyhat = Burn 1 Cracker  
Purple partyhat = Burn 5 Crackers
